  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The main purpose of the project is to increase household food security through practicing conservation agriculture principles that can boost yields in their field, improvement of saving and loaning culture that can give the communities opportunities to meet some of the basic needs at household level. This plan is intended to empower the communities and farmers with skills and knowledge so as to increase ability to economically become sustainable all this can be done through training the communities, setting demonstration gardens and construction of sand dams.</narrative>
